text: The Diplomatic Pouch () is a 1927 Soviet silent thriller movie directed by Alexander Dovzhenko.Курьерный ростСУМКА ДИПКУРЬЕРА It stars M. Buyukli, A. Klymenko, and Heorhii Zelondzhev-Shypov. ==Actors== *M. Buyukli as Embassy Secretary *A.
